body: Would give five but I have only just planted it so waiting for spring, if it’s as good as the others iv bought then it will be five stars , beautiful rose tree and excellent service from David Austin Roses

Received in good time. Perfect looking standard rose. Healthy. Now planted and waiting for the magic to happen. Only thing I have noticed is a bit of die back but I suspect that's more to do with more care taking than any fault of DA. 
Really.looking forward to it flowering.
